---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Project" description="Wyoming Coal-to-Ammonia Initiative - Next-generation industrial manufacturing with full carbon integration.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative bg-navy-950 text-white overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
      <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width=\"60\" height=\"60\" viewBox=\"0 0 60 60\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"%3E%3Cg fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"%3E%3Cg fill=\"%23ffffff\" fill-opacity=\"1\"%3E%3Cpath d=\"M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z\"/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E');"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-24 md:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gold-500 mb-8"></div>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight tracking-tight">
          Wyoming Coal-to-Ammonia<br />
          <span class="text-gold-500">Initiative</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-8 text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
          Next-generation industrial manufacturing with full carbon integration.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-gold-600 via-gold-500 to-gold-600"></div>
  </section>

  <!-- Project Overview -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-gold-700 mb-4">Overview</h2>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900">Project Summary</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed font-serif">
          CapStone's marquee initiative is a Coal-to-Ammonia project sited in Wyoming — a next-generation industrial facility converting regional coal resources into blue ammonia and dispatchable power generation, while integrating carbon capture and geological storage.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          The project utilizes 21st-century gasification processes to produce low-carbon intensity ammonia at scale.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why This Matters -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-gold-700 mb-4">Strategic Importance</h2>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900">Why This Matters</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- National Security -->
        <div class="bg-white border-t-4 border-crimson-600 shadow-lg">
          <div class="p-8">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy-900 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-gold-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">National Security</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Domestic ammonia production reduces reliance on foreign supply chains for a critical industrial input.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Food Supply Chain -->
        <div class="bg-white border-t-4 border-crimson-600 shadow-lg">
          <div class="p-8">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy-900 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-gold-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">Food Supply Chain</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Approximately 80% of global ammonia production supports agricultural fertilizer. Stable domestic supply protects American food security.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Clean Energy Transition -->
        <div class="bg-white border-t-4 border-crimson-600 shadow-lg">
          <div class="p-8">
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-navy-900 flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-gold-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy-900 mb-4">Clean Energy Transition</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              Blue ammonia is emerging as a carbon-free fuel source. Demand is projected to grow significantly in the coming decade.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Project Status -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-gold-700 mb-4">Current Phase</h2>
        <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900">Project Status</h3>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-navy-900 text-white p-10 border-l-4 border-gold-500">
        <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">
          The project is currently in structured <strong class="text-gold-500">Pre-FEED development</strong>, leveraging Wyoming's emerging CO&#8322; storage regulatory framework and existing industrial fertilizer infrastructure.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Wyoming -->
  <section class="py-24 bg-navy-950 text-white relative">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
      <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background-image: url('data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg width=\"60\" height=\"60\" viewBox=\"0 0 60 60\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\"%3E%3Cg fill=\"none\" fill-rule=\"evenodd\"%3E%3Cg fill=\"%23ffffff\" fill-opacity=\"1\"%3E%3Cpath d=\"M36 34v-4h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2h-4zm0-30V0h-2v4h-4v2h4v4h2V6h4V4h-4zM6 34v-4H4v4H0v2h4v4h2v-4h4v-2H6zM6 4V0H4v4H0v2h4v4h2V6h4V4H6z\"/%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/g%3E%3C/svg%3E');"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div>
          <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gold-500 mb-8"></div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Why Wyoming</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
            Wyoming offers a unique combination of abundant coal resources, established industrial infrastructure, and regulatory leadership in carbon storage — making it the ideal location for next-generation energy manufacturing.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-navy-900 p-6 border border-navy-700">
            <div class="text-gold-500 text-3xl font-bold mb-2">#1</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Coal Producer</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-navy-900 p-6 border border-navy-700">
            <div class="text-gold-500 text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Class VI</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Primacy State</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-navy-900 p-6 border border-navy-700">
            <div class="text-gold-500 text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Pro</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Business Climate</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-navy-900 p-6 border border-navy-700">
            <div class="text-gold-500 text-3xl font-bold mb-2">Strategic</div>
            <div class="text-sm text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-wide">Infrastructure</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-100">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="w-16 h-1 bg-gold-500 mx-auto mb-8"></div>
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-navy-900">Interested in partnership opportunities?</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">We welcome discussions with qualified partners and investors.</p>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-10 py-4 bg-navy-900 hover:bg-navy-800 text-gold-500 font-semibold tracking-wide uppercase text-sm transition-colors border border-navy-900 hover:border-gold-500"
        >
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
